gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;状态中302、403、 500、&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;200&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;、404、502&lt;/span&gt;代码含义？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 15px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;一二三四五原则: 一. 消息系列&amp;nbsp; 二. 成功系列&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; 三. 重定向系列 四. 请求错误系列&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; 五. 服务器端错误系列 &amp;nbsp;302:临时转移成功，请求的内容已转移到新位置 403:禁止访问 500:服务器内部错误 401代表未授权。&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: gray; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;200&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: gray; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;是请求成功，404是文件未找到，502是服务器内部错误。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 15px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 15px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 15px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;MyISAM&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;和 InnoDB 的基本区别？索引结构如何实现？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 15px; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;MyISAM&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;类型不支持事务处理等高级处理，而InnoDB类型支持。MyISAM类型的表强调的是性能，其执行速度比InnoDB类型更快，但是不提供事务支持，而InnoDB提供事务支持以及外部键等高级数据库功能。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 15px; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;创建索引：alert table tablename add index (`字段名`)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 15px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 15px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;include&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;与require的区别?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 15px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;1.include()&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;在执行文件时每次都要进行读取和评估&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 15px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; require()&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;文件只处理一次(实际上文件内容替换了require()语句)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 15px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;2.require()&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;通常放在PHP脚本程序的最前面&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 15px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; include()&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;的使用和require()一样,一般放在流程控制的处理区段中,PHP脚本文件读到include()语句时,才将它包含的文件读进来,这种方式,可以把程序执行时的流程简单化&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 15px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;3,require()&lt;/span